ces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9977d3f2a343dfcc17ff153973db395916d21a7","tid":94954,"uid":34311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係幾年前 <br />\n我同一個寡婦結左婚 <br />\n佢有一個已成年既女 <br />\n後來嫁左比我老豆 <br />\n<br />\n咁我繼女就做左我後媽 <br />\n而我老豆就做左我女婿 <br />\n<br />\n兩年後我老婆同我生左一個仔 <br />\n佢係我後媽既同母異父既細路 <br />\n我個仔叫我「老豆」 <br />\n我就叫我個仔「舅父」 <br />\n<br />\n我繼女又為我老豆生左一個仔 <br />\n佢係我細路 <br />\n但佢又要叫我外公 <br />\n<br />\n我係我老婆個老公 <br />\n但係我老婆係我後媽個阿媽喎 <br />\n所以我係自己既外公 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到左新年 <br />\n黎料啦 <br />\n<br />\n我就同我後媽同我老豆 <br />\n即係同我繼女同女婿交換利是 <br />\n<br />\n我封廿蚊比我個仔 <br />\n佢話:「多謝老豆!」 <br />\n我又答返佢:「唔洗、舅父!係呢，咁我果封呢?」 <br />\n「你都痴線，我結左婚啦咩?」唉，我自己都亂左... <br />\n<br />\n食團年飯果陣 <br />\n我係抬面上面放左一封一千蚊利是 <br />\n再拎返封利是上手 <br />\n叫左聲 :「多謝外公!」 <br />\n<br />\n好彩唔係街姐 <br />\n唔係真係比人捉去青山訓一排 <br />\n而家諗返自己真係痴痴地線 <br />\n自己比錢自己洗 <br />\n咪即係去自己鋪頭買野...</blockquote><br />\n次次睇都睇到成頭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明明睇過幾次都仲笑得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ed125cb0c272643722ba457ecf29c68110ee93","tid":94954,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:27:05.000Z","msg":"告佢老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas